Nemesis Enforcer/Koga Shuko/Oblitertron/Hades/Anubis/Unitron/Scattershot:

(Code, post the damage for the base, and what was Plintissa aiming at?  
Please be a little more specific about stuff like that)

Oblitertron cried out as shots hit his left cheek, Dark One losing control, 
Pyro taking control.  Laughing evily in a deep voice, swinging his hands in a 
backhand to try and knock off the heads (knock them away), one of the heads 
bit Oblitertron's shoulder (hope you don't take that as moding), taking an 
energon saber from subspace, Oblitertron swung upwards at the neck, firing 
two powerful optic blasts at Radistor's back, firing a burst of flames in a 
kind of wave so they go at three of his heads, raising his plasma rifle and 
firing two shots off at the base of one of the necks, another kick to the 
right like a wrecking ball at the badly damaged (I'm assuming it is from the 
constant beating)  
---------------
Nemesis Enforcer raised his missile launcher, firing off a rocket at the now 
in dino-mode Radistor's front left leg.
--------------
Koga Shuko raised his missile launcher firing off a missile at the space in 
between two autoguns, jumping to the side as enemy fire knicked his left foot.
--------------
Hades fired off a rocket at the 'chest' area of the dino-mode gestalt 
(Radistor).
-------------
Anubis pulled out his plasma rifle, firing off a rocket at one of Radistor's 
faces, firing off a few plasma blasts at the autoguns.
-------------
Scattershot, up in the air, took out two charges, chucking them down at 
Suukie, each set to explode on impact.  Taking out a homemade bomb, with the 
strength of three missiles from a rocket launcher, dropped the bomb down at 
the middle of Raditor's back.
